{"topicId": "tree-traversals", "aids": [{"id": "mem-order", "type": "mnemonic", "title": "Traversal Orders", "content": "**In**order: **In** the middle (L-N-R)\n**Pre**order: N **Pre**cedes (N-L-R)\n**Post**order: N **Post**poned (L-R-N)", "forRemembering": "DFS traversal orders"}, {"id": "mem-dfs-bfs", "type": "tip", "title": "DFS = Stack, BFS = Queue", "content": "DFS (Deep): uses Stack (LIFO)\nBFS (Broad): uses Queue (FIFO)\n\nRecursion implicitly uses stack!", "forRemembering": "Data structures for traversals"}]}
